去大媽到。 <br />\n<br />\n又或者⋯⋯ 整番個 thisdaima 或 大媽 youtube channel，<br />\n定期請大媽放片整LIVE，<br />\n比D 呀伯日日J<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n從中收廣告費，<br />\n又可以減低風化案<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等等⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n希望大家連登仔義士出多D計仔，<br />\n善用呢D機會去補貼番自己友資金，<br />\n做埋長期經濟戰準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：幫朋友開PO 佢係經濟學家來，以上係為左促進香港經濟增長"},{"pid":"e756de4b81e7aed3f03c10795831ca446f9f8c41","tid":1301408,"uid":69120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:45:16.000Z","msg":"pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8ec726cd8b543c89c704ed633f2cc99b6e2d1b","tid":1301408,"uid":69120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"推到有人應"},{"pid":"d45a12023a0bf23c839459551bcb735082df60fc","tid":1301408,"uid":160988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:03:13.000Z","msg":"諗法幾好<br />\n賺藍絲癈老錢<br />\n但唔係好想同d雞合作"},{"pid":"bd90e2748a2cb08d0cf02798e8397bd08202bb06","tid":1301408,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d45a12023a0bf23c839459551bcb735082df60fc","tid":1301408,"uid":160988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:03:13.000Z","msg":"諗法幾好<br />\n賺藍絲癈老錢<br />\n但唔係好想同d雞合作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"咁都串到社生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df809c3bd5e8bae1fdb71bb97adc58d6af09b35a","tid":1301408,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:08:02.000Z","msg":"贏到區議會仲實際，大把資源可以用"},{"pid":"c14ca20584e2aa64f29d1f9f8b8dc62a903f217c","tid":1301408,"uid":181033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:12:09.000Z","msg":"以物易物？<br />\n巴打可唔可以解釋下有何差異"}]}